<h1>Mujeres: Grandes Protagonistas del Estallido Social</h1>
<p>Author: Revolución Obrera</p>
<p>Time: 2023-03-01T10:13:07-05:00</p>
<p>Images: ['<a href="https://www.revolucionobrera.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/118501188_lamona.jpg">118501188_lamona.jpg</a>', '<a href="https://www.revolucionobrera.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/Mujeres-PR.jpg">Mujeres-PR.jpg</a>']</p>
